296
00:21:35,043 --> 00:21:36,419
Clarice, phone.

297
00:21:36,503 --> 00:21:37,920
It's the guru.
Crawford?

298
00:21:38,005 --> 00:21:39,130
Yeah.
Thanks, Ardelia.

299
00:21:39,631 --> 00:21:40,631
Starling?

300
00:21:40,716 --> 00:21:41,882
CLARICE: Sir?

301
00:21:42,259 --> 00:21:43,718
Miggs is dead.

302
00:21:44,845 --> 00:21:47,471
Dead? How?

303
