The orderly heard Lecter
whispering to him
all afternoon,

304
00:21:50,892 --> 00:21:51,934
and Miggs crying.

305
00:21:52,019 --> 00:21:53,144
They found him
at bed check.

306
00:21:53,228 --> 00:21:55,021
