I would ask my
driver to help you,

339
00:23:26,655 --> 00:23:28,989
but he detests
physical labor.

340
00:23:29,991 --> 00:23:31,158
Great.

341
00:23:31,743 --> 00:23:34,495
You just stay here.
I'll be back in
