429
00:31:29,762 --> 00:31:32,639
but how long can you
and old Jackie boy wait?

430
00:31:33,057 --> 00:31:35,058
Our little Billy must
already be searching

431
00:31:35,143 --> 00:31:38,061
for that next
special lady.

432
00:31:38,730 --> 00:31:42,190
After all it was
a great big world

433
