00:33:23,084 --> 00:33:24,209
Would you?

451
00:33:24,293 --> 00:33:25,419
Sure.

452
00:33:26,337 --> 00:33:28,005
Thank you.
That's all right.

453
00:33:28,089 --> 00:33:29,256
You look kind
