00:37:02,511 --> 00:37:04,846
Look at him, Starling.
Tell me what you see.

508
00:37:06,349 --> 00:37:07,891
Well, he's a white male.

509
00:37:07,975 --> 00:37:09,059
Serial killers tend to hunt

510
00:37:09,143 --> 00:37:10,769
